{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM04_300.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1d,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Leon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, welcome. I have some really good stuff for sale today, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "(When it comes to clothes, Leon would know best. I should ask her about clothes for Plachta.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Um, actually there's something I wanted to ask you today. I want you to make some clothes for Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Plachta... You mean that talking book? You want clothes for a book...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I got it! You want a book cover?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Um, not exactly. You see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You're turning a book into a doll... I see. Alchemy is really convenient, isn't it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Okay, this sounds like fun. Count me in."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Thank you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, no need for thanks. I'm going to need to take measurements, so can you show me the doll?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh, about that... It's not ready yet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see. That's a problem..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Uu, I'm sorry... I know I'm the one who asked..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "...Wait a minute. I just thought of something interesting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "If we don't know about the size of the doll, we can just make adjustable clothes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x52,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "You can do that!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Yup, by using highly elastic cloth. They'll be clothes that can stretch and shrink."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "That way, it wouldn't matter if the size of the doll changes a little either. She'd still be able to wear it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I see... I never thought of that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Hehe. Anyway, there's something I'll need you to do, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "You need to make the cloth I just mentioned."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Huh...!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "You can find cloth that's kind of elastic just about anywhere. But it needs to be even more elastic."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "That's why we need special cloth. I know how to make it, but I don't know if I'd be able to make it myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "But I think you'd have no problem making it. What do you think?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "If you know how to make it... I think I can do it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "That's good. I'll tell you what to do, and you take care of the rest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I understand. I'll bring it to you when it's done."
        }
    ]
}